661
00:50:14,800 --> 00:50:18,136
I don't think there's enough being done
by the game to synthesize its left-wing

662
00:50:18,160 --> 00:50:22,295
elements into a conclusion about the
nature of our world.

663
00:50:22,319 --> 00:50:26,376
