Shinra is the problem and not capitalism

666
00:50:36,000 --> 00:50:42,295
generally, limiting the scope of the game's
message to a specific evil inside of its own world.

667
00:50:42,319 --> 00:50:47,335
However, I will say that Final Fantasy
VII is a damn fine game,

668
00:50:47,359 --> 00:50:54,376
